snippet.title: GoPro Hero3+ Black Edition
snippet.description: Like the Hero3, the GoPro Hero3+ Black Edition's strongest attributes are its excellent video quality and impressive list of shooting options. If that's what matters most to you, this is the action cam to get.

snippet.title: Sony Cyber-shot DSC-HX400V
snippet.description: Its lens, sensor, and LCD remain unchanged from its predecessor, but a new processor, Wi-Fi, and GPS keep the flagship megazoom from getting stale.

snippet.title: iOn Air Pro 3
snippet.description: A fun, flexible action cam, the iOn Air Pro 3 keeps things simple without sacrificing video or build quality, making it an excellent option for those who just want to go out and shoot -- in or out of the water.

snippet.title: An Amazon Prime price bump means fist pumps at Netflix
snippet.description: Amazon is considering a Prime rate increase, and it would push the cost higher than Netflix for the first time. That's good news for Netflix, but -- like Prime's combo of services -- it's a little complicated.

snippet.title: Mini space robot could run on mud
snippet.description: Navy researchers explore the concept of operating two-pound "microrover" robots that are powered by long-running microbial fuel cells to explore planetary bodies in space.

snippet.title: 3D printer pumps out items in many materials and hues
snippet.description: Stratasys' Objet500 Connex3 3D printer is capable of creating products in one print job that are rigid, flexible, and come in hundreds of colors.

snippet.title: GPS gets elderly couple stuck in mud for 2 days
snippet.description: A California couple wonders whether their GPS is sending them down the right road. It isn't. But they keep going anyway. Then they are mired.

snippet.title: Samsung Galaxy Admire 2 pumps up the music
snippet.description: Muve Music and a good camera make this midrange LTE Android a keeper, though the phone does have some faults.

snippet.title: Olloclip 4-in-1 Photo Lens pumps up iPhone pics
snippet.description: This convenient, ultraportable add-on lens updates the company's line with a second macro. You'll also find fish-eye and wide-angle lenses.

snippet.title: Video app Squrl pumps up content with redesign
snippet.description: The video-discovery app that scours the Internet improves its search and adds private messaging. The next step is getting official with content providers.
